# Combinatronics Cheat Sheet

### 
nPn = n! (permutation of n things in n positions)
nPr = n!/(n-r)!    (permutation of n things in r positions)
nCr = n!/((n-r)!*r*)



## n!
```c++
///EASIER CODE
int fact(int n)
{
      if(n==0)
      return 1;
    int res = 1;
    for (int i = 2; i <= n; i++)
        res = res * i;
    return res;
}


```
